/go\/sunnycars-en-albania\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>. Free cancellation up to 1 hour before rental start and insurances are included (so no surprises when collecting your car).&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-albania\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144104\/tirana-albania-route-1.jpg\" alt=\"albania itinerary tirana\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"albania itinerary tirana\" class=\"wp-image-87761 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144104\/tirana-albania-route-1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144104\/tirana-albania-route-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144104\/tirana-albania-route-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144104\/tirana-albania-route-1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144104\/tirana-albania-route-1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144104\/tirana-albania-route-1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144104\/tirana-albania-route-1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144104\/tirana-albania-route-1-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144104\/tirana-albania-route-1-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144104\/tirana-albania-ro