ock-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16162927\/albania-guide-2-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16162927\/albania-guide-2-338x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Albania Itinerary: Complete 2-Week Road Trip\" height=\"600\" width=\"338\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-where-to-stay-in-berat\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/berat-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Where to Stay in Berat<\/a><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>When you reach Berat, book yourself into a traditional guesthouse. We recommend staying in the neighborhood of Gorica as it&#x2019;s more affordable and only just across the bridge from the town center.&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/berat-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See all your hotel options here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tradita-e-beratit-hotel\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Tradita e Beratitu\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https: