ir.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15171642\/berat-albania-route-1-22x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15171642\/berat-albania-route-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Unusually, two neighborhoods face each other across the water with bridges connecting them, so it&#x2019;s fun to move between the areas, wandering the charming cobbled streets. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Make sure to also walk up to the impressive Byzantine Church and the castle ruins, which are left at the top of the hill&#x2014;it&#x2019;s the perfect place to go for views of the valley below, especially at sunset.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172447\/berat-albania-route-9.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-87488 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172447\/berat-albania-route-9.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172447\/berat-albania-route-9-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172447\/berat-albania-route-9-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172447\/berat-albania-route-9-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/20