apper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1.jpg\" alt=\"albania itinerary blue eye\"><\/noscript><img width=\"247\" height=\"338\" alt=\"albania itinerary blue eye\" class=\"wp-image-87494 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1405px) 100vw, 1405px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1.jpg 1405w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-439x600.jpg 439w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-593x810.jpg 593w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-247x338.jpg 247w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-119x163.jpg 119w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-132x180.jpg 132w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-562x768.jpg 562w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-749x1024.jpg 749w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-790x1080.jpg 790w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-1054x1440.jpg 1054w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-300x410.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-600x820.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-150x205.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1-22x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15172919\/blue-eye-albania-route-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It takes just 30 minutes to drive here from Gjirokaster and then a 15-minute walk from the parking spot. When you arrive, you&#x2019;ll be met by the most gorgeous sight: beautiful blue and green colored water that comes fresh from a natural spring. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The water is numbingly cold but so refreshing, especially in the summer! It does say that you&#x2019;re not allowed to swim, but plenty of people do so (there was a guard there patrolling, and he only asked people not to jump from the platform). We recommend arriving as early as possible in the morning to avoid the summer crowds.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Entrance fee:<\/strong> 50 LEK (0.50 USD)<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3.jpg\" alt=\"blue eye albania travel guide\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"blue eye albania travel guide\" class=\"wp-image-88125 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-20x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>After your swim, dry off and head back to the car for the rest of your trip. Follow the road to Saranda, and continue on to Ksamil from there. From the Blue Eye, the journey takes approximately 1 hour.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Ksamil and Saranda are neighboring coastal towns and both popular choices on an Albania itinerary. However, Sarande is much more of a party town than Ksamil, so it depends on your preference.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-how-to-get-from-gjirokaster-to-ksamil\">How to get from Gjirokaster to Ksamil<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<h5 id=\"h-by-car-2\">By Car:<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>The drive from Gjirokaster to Ksamil takes around 1 hour and 20 minutes. However, that doesn&#x2019;t include time for your stop at the Blue Eye. Allow for 2 hours at the Blue Eye to relax, have a swim, and enjoy walking through nature.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2.jpg\" alt=\"blue eye albania\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"blue eye albania\" class=\"wp-image-88123 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2-20x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115503\/blue-eye-albania-route-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h5 id=\"h-by-bus-2\">By Bus:<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>There are no direct buses running from Gjirokaster to Ksamil. Instead, you will need to take a bus to Saranda and from there take a taxi to Ksamil. Buses leave Gjirokaster every 20-30 minutes and take about 1 hour.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#x2019;re traveling by bus, you won&#x2019;t be able to make a stop off at Syri I Kalt&#xEB;r (Blue Eye). However, tours run regularly from Gjirokaster and Saranda and include return transport.<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div data-vi-partner-id=\"P00037894\" data-vi-language=\"en\" data-vi-currency=\"USD\" data-vi-partner-type=\"AFFILIATE\" data-vi-url=\"121020P3,121028P1,121020P7\" data-vi-campaign=\"albania-itinerary-widget\" class=\"lazyload block-viator\" data-script=\"https:\/\/www.viator.com\/orion\/partner\/widget.js\"><\/div>\n            \n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-where-to-stay-in-ksamil\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/ksamil-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Where to stay in Ksamil<\/a><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you arrive in Ksamil, choose to stay close to the beaches, ideally within 10 to 15 minutes walk. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/ksamil-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See all your hotel options here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/ionian-hotel\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Ionian Hotel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15230154\/Ionian-Hotel-450x210.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Ionian Hotel<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/summer-point-hotel\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Summer Point Hotel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/15230603\/Summer-Point-Hotel-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Summer Point Hotel<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-day-6-ksamil\">Day 6: Ksamil<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The beach paradise of Ksamil is a must-see on your Albania itinerary. Sitting on the coast of the Albanian Riviera, it&#x2019;s home to incredible beaches, which aren&#x2019;t dissimilar to the south of France (hence the name!). Turquoise ocean backs onto soft yellow sand that&#x2019;s covered in a sea of multi-colored beach umbrellas&#x2014;bliss! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16152815\/ksamil-albania-route-7.jpg\" alt=\"sunset beautiful beach albania\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sunset beautiful beach albania\" class=\"wp-image-87844 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16152815\/ksamil-albania-route-7.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16152815\/ksamil-albania-route-7-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16152815\/ksamil-albania-route-7-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16152815\/ksamil-albania-route-7-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16152815\/ksamil-albania-route-7-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16152815\/ksamil-albania-route-7-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16152815\/ksamil-albania-route-7-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16152815\/ksamil-albania-route-7-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022