avel-blog\/best-unesco-world-heritage-sites\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">UNESCO World Heritage Site<\/a>. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16153829\/butrint-national-park-albania-route-3.jpg\" alt=\"butrint national park albania itinerary\"><\/noscript><img width=\"233\" height=\"338\" alt=\"butrint national park albania itinerary\" class=\"wp-image-87854 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1323px) 100vw, 1323px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16153829\/butrint-national-park-albania-route-3.jpg 1323w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16153829\/butrint-national-park-albania-route-3-413x600.jpg 413w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16153829\/butrint-national-park-albania-route-3-558x810.jpg 558w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16153829\/butrint-national-park-albania-route-3-233x338.jpg 233w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16153829\/butrint-national-park-albania-route-3-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16153829\/butrint-national-park-albania-route-3-112x163.jpg 112w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16153829\/butrint-national-park-albania-route-3-124x180.jpg 124w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16153829\/butrint-national-park-albania-route-3-529x768.jpg 529w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16153829\/butrint-national-park-albania-route-3-706x1024.jpg 706w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16153829\/butrint-national-park-albania-route-3-744x1080.jpg 744w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/u