er\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150004\/theth-albania-route-10.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>People come to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/albania\/theth\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Theth<\/a> to camp and hike, so it&#x2019;s popular in summer with tourists. However, you&#x2019;ll notice that authentic local life continues, with the farmers still herding their sheep and horses along the roads. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16145815\/theth-albania-route-1.jpg\" alt=\"albania itinerary theth\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"albania itinerary theth\" class=\"wp-image-87796 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16145815\/theth-albania-route-1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16145815\/theth-albania-route-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16145815\/theth-albania-route-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16145815\/theth-albania-route-1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16145815\/theth-albania-route-1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16145815\/theth-albania-route-1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16145815\/theth-albania-route-1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16145815\/theth-albania-route-1-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourha