age size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4.jpg\" alt=\"albania itinerary drive to theth\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"319\" alt=\"albania itinerary drive to theth\" class=\"wp-image-87820 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4-800x567.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4-1080x765.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4-450x319.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4-163x115.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4-254x180.jpg 254w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4-768x544.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4-1024x725.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4-1440x1020.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4-300x213.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4-600x425.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4-150x106.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4-30x21.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150950\/theth-albania-route-4.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h5 id=\"h-by-bus-6\">By Bus:<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>As Theth is very remote, there are no buses from Kruje to Theth. You&#x2019;ll need to get to Shkoder and arrange a transfer or organized tour from there to Theth.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div data-vi-partner-id=\"P00037894\" data-vi-language=\"en\" data-vi-currency=\"USD\" data-vi-partner-type=\"AFFILIATE\" data-vi-url=\"16080P5,150064P2\" data-vi-campaign=\"albania-itinerary-widget\" class=\"lazyload block-viator\" data-script=\"https:\/\/www.viator.com\/orion\/partner\/widget.js\"><\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-day-12-hike-to-valbona-peak-theth\">Day 12: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/albania\/theth\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Hike to Valbona Peak, Theth<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Day 12 is your chance to explore the unbelievable nature that Albania has to offer. Pack a backpack and prepare to do the most beautiful hike from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/albania\/theth\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Theth<\/a> to Valbona peak and back. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150021\/theth-albania-route-11.jpg\" alt=\"albania itinerary Theth to Valbona peak hike\"><\/noscript><img width=\"256\" height=\"338\" alt=\