ads\/2022\/08\/16145947\/theth-albania-route-9.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-how-long-does-the-hike-take\">How long does the hike take?&#xA0;<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Start at 8 AM, and you should return to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/albania\/theth\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Theth<\/a> around 3-4 PM. It takes around 7 hours to hike the trail (15 km in total), and it&#x2019;s doable but definitely a challenge! Please be aware that on some parts of the trail, there are (very) steep gravel paths, so make sure you&#x2019;re wearing proper hiking shoes.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Traveling to Theth by public transport? You can catch a ferry or shared van back to Shkoder after your hike (the journey is approx 2 hours).<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150034\/theth-albania-route-12.jpg\" alt=\"albania Theth Valbona peak hike cafe\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"albania Theth Valbona peak hike cafe\" class=\"wp-image-87812 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16150034\/theth-albania-route-12.jpg 128