50034\/theth-albania-route-12.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-day-13-theth-to-tirana\">Day 13: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/albania\/theth\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Theth<\/a> to Tirana<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>On your penultimate day in Albania, it&#x2019;s time to head back to the buzzing capital: Tirana (a must-see on your 2-week Albania itinerary). Have breakfast and make an early start to drive back to Tirana so you can spend the afternoon in the city.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12.jpg\" alt=\"albania itinerary tirana capital city\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"albania itinerary tirana capital city\" class=\"wp-image-87785 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12-20x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144539\/tirana-albania-route-12.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4>Spend the Afternoon in Tirana<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#x2019;ve checked into your hotel, make the most of the city&#x2019;s cultural hotspots, enjoying all the museums, art galleries, and interesting restaurants. You&#x2019;ll find the National Museum of History here, which is a plot of former underground bunkers now turned into an exhibit on Albania&#x2019;s communist history. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Entry Fee:<\/strong> 400 LEK (3.50 USD)<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144414\/tirana-albania-route-5.jpg\" alt=\"albania itinerary tirana bunk art\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"albania itinerary tirana bunk art\" class=\"wp-image-87772 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144414\/tirana-albania-route-5.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144414\/tirana-albania-route-5-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144414\/tirana-albania-route-5-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144414\/tirana-albania-route-5-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144414\/tirana-albania-route-5-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144414\/tirana-albania-route-5-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144414\/tirana-albania-route-5-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144414\/tirana-albania-route-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144414\/tirana-albania-route-5-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16144414\/tirana-albania-route-5-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads