19;s possible to take a bus from Theth to Tirana. You&#x2019;ll need to first take a shared shuttle bus to Shkoder (or taxi). From there, there are buses running every 30 minutes to Tirana. The journey takes 2 hours and costs 400 LEK (3.60 USD), so it&#x2019;s very cheap.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-where-to-stay-in-tirana\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tirana-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Where to Stay in Tirana<\/a><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The Blloku neighborhood is the most colorful and trendy of all and a great place to stay in Tirana. Alternatively, anywhere close to the city center is good. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tirana-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See all your hotel options in Tirana<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotel-theatro\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Hotel Theatro\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16115649\/Hotel-Theatro-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Hotel Theatro<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotel-boutique-vila\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <im