and tourists head for the beach, and it can get very busy. Because of this, we recommend visiting in the shoulder seasons: May\/June or September. This is the perfect time to enjoy warm weather, sunny days, and the beaches of the Albanian Riviera without the crowds. It also has slightly cooler temperatures, which are perfect for hiking in the mountains.&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1.jpg\" alt=\" best time to travel albania\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\" best time to travel albania\" class=\"wp-image-88157 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1-20x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17121336\/himare-albania-route-8-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-is-albania-safe\">Is Albania Safe?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There is some dispute about whether Albania is safe, and its communist history has slightly tarnished its reputation. However, in our personal experience, it&#x2019;s very safe. The locals are warm, friendly people who are always eager to help, and the towns feel very safe and inviting. We walked around with our phones and cameras the entire time, zero issues! Albania truly has our hearts. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#x2019;ve met a lot of solo (female) travelers who had the best time. Yes, they got some heads turning but never experienced anything negative. Obviously, take care of yourself and stay inside the main tourist areas. Here are our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-safety\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">tips on how to travel safely<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1.jpg\" alt=\"safe albania travel itinerary\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"safe albania travel itinerary\" class=\"wp-image-87755 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/16143528\/albania-route-1-150x188.jpg 150w\" t